/*E*/
/*S*/ Kurzbeschreibung
@NODE "Overview" "FreshBar-Guide / Overview"
@{bpen 4}@{FG HIGHLIGHT}@{b}1. Overview @{ub}@{FG TEXT}@{bpen 0}

@{par}@{FG FILL}@{apen 11}@{b}The programm FreshBar provides progress-bars accessable
via ARexx.@{ub}@{apen 1}@{FG TEXT}

@{par}@{u}Features@{uu}:
@{par}· Freeware
@{par}· Handles as many windows as you want.
@{par}· Every window can contain as many bars as you want.
@{par}· Fontsensitive
@{par}
@{par}Its allowed to include FreshBar in own projects.
@{par}The complete source-code (for StormC 3.0) is included and can be used without
@{par}any limits.
@{par}
@ENDNODE
/*E*/
/*S*/ Installation
@node "Installation" "FreshBar-Anleitung / Installation"
@{bpen 4}@{FG HIGHLIGHT}@{b}2. Installation@{ub}@{FG TEXT}@{bpen 0}

@{par}There isn't much to install. All you need to use FreshBar
via ARexx is that FreshBar and RexxMast are already running.

You should start FreshBar with "run >nil: FreshBar". So you can
continue working with the same shell process.

To copy the FreshBar executable into your C:-directory, just click here @{" Install " SYSTEM "copy /FreshBar C:"}.

@endnode
/*E*/
/*S*/ Requirements
@NODE "Voraussetzungen" "FreshBar-Anleitung / Voraussetzungen"
@{bpen 4}@{FG HIGHLIGHT}@{b}3. Requirements for FreshBar.@{ub}@{FG TEXT}@{bpen 0}

@{par}To use FreshBar RexxMast needs to be running.
You can find RexxMast in your "SYS:System/"-directory.
@{par}Last but not least min. OS 3.0 is necessary.

@{par}Probably you will only be able to compile the included source-codes
using the great StormC++-compiler.

@ENDNODE
/*E*/
/*S*/ Beschreibung
@NODE "Description" "FreshBar-Guide / Description"
@{bpen 4}@{FG HIGHLIGHT}@{b}4. Description@{ub}@{FG TEXT}@{bpen 0}

@{par} Once started FreshBar will wait for ARexx-commands.

@{par} FreshBar provides the following ARexx-commands:
@{par} @{" ABOUT " link "ABOUT"}
@{par} @{" QUIT " link "QUIT"}
@{par} @{" CREATEBARWINDOW " link "CREATEBARWINDOW"}
@{par} @{" DELETEBARWINDOW " link "DELETEBARWINDOW"}
@{par} @{" OPENBARWINDOW " link "OPENBARWINDOW"}
@{par} @{" CLOSEBARWINDOW " link "CLOSEBARWINDOW"}
@{par} @{" CLOSEALLBARWINDOWS " link "CLOSEALLBARWINDOWS"}
@{par} @{" SETBARWINDOWWIDTH " link "SETBARWINDOWWIDTH"}
@{par} @{" SETBARWINDOWPOS " link "SETBARWINDOWPOS"}
@{par} @{" ADDBAR " link "ADDBAR"}
@{par} @{" REMOVEBAR " link "REMOVEBAR"}
@{par} @{" SETCURRENT " link "SETCURRENT"}
@{par} @{" SETMAXIMUM " link "SETMAXIMUM"}
@{par} @{" SETFILLPEN " link "SETFILLPEN"}
@{par} @{" SETBACKPEN " link "SETBACKPEN"}
@{par} @{" SETPROGRESSMODE " link "SETPROGRESSMODE"}
@{par} @{" TESTOKBUTTON " link "TESTOKBUTTON"}


@ENDNODE
/*E*/
/*S*/ Bekannte Fehler
@NODE "KnownBugs" "FreshBar-Guide / Knownbugs"
@{bpen 4}@{FG HIGHLIGHT}@{b}4. Known bugs@{ub}@{FG TEXT}@{bpen 0}

@{par}@{APEN 11}Windowtitles with blanks lead to crashes@{APEN 1}
@{par}Since the OS-function ReadArgs() can not handle strings with
blanks it is not possible to use blanks in FreshBar-windowtitles and
button-texts. This can end up in a systemcrash.
This does NOT affect the bartitle.

@{par}If you discover any other bugs please contact me: @{" Addresse " link "Adresse"}

@ENDNODE
/*E*/
/*S*/ Thanks
